<br>
I also already have the Robe of the Oracle and will most likley camp the SMR for exp in the high 40's with some friends.  Ultimatley I'd like to be able to finish the epic immediatley after the General kill and by lvl 52. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uevertorn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Evertorn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/14/01 1:07:41 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: When to Start</span><hr size=1> Yup, I suggest Founy first, because if you fail, the zone line is very close.  Where as with Tani, you'll probably die because the zone line is so far away. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uteramenor.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Teramenor</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/15/01 7:57:26 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: When to Start</span><hr size=1> I don't know whether your level affects your chances at pickpocketing, though I wouldn't have started that low - I did my epic pickpocketing at levels 47 and 48, and never once got aggroed by either Founy or Tani. I also had a PP of 200 the whole time. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=litomi>Litomi</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/16/01 1:01:27 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: When to Start</span><hr size=1> I pp'd my first piece off the Kaladim guy at lvl 38 with 170ish skill.  Got the one from the DE guy 2nd try at lvl 50.  I dont think level matters much, just skill. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ugalidaddv.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Galidadd V</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/16/01 8:37:12 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: When to Start</span><hr size=1> I did the pick pocketing at lvl 49 but I started with 134 skill. I meant to start this low and knew I would have aggro. I never attempted Tani until my skill was 190+ and I was lvl 50. It took me about 10 spawns on Founy to get the page and he aggroed me MANY times. The other miners also aggro and hit very hard. With Tani I died once and then went back and for kicks tryed one more time. I got the page on one of his many despawn respawn routines.<br>
<br>
All I need now is the frikkin book in Hate and I can move on.<br>
<br>
Galidadd Vyleshayde<br>
Rake of 51 Gardens <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><br><font color=#FF0000>- </font><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse>The Safehouse</a><font color=#FF0000> - </font><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13>Quests of Norrath</a> <font color=#FF0000> - </font><a href="http://www.thesafehouse.org">The Safehouse website</a><font color=#FF0000> - </font> <center><a href="http://www.guildboss.com"><img
